  "body": "* **I'm submitting a ...**\r\n\r\n  * \\[x] Feature request\r\n  * \\[ ] Bug report\r\n\r\n* **Feature Request**\r\n\r\n  * I'm using MEW in offline mode for my cold wallet\r\n  * With the \"Send Offline\" feature, I can easily sign arbitrary transactions on mainnet, including contract calls (with custom \"Data\")\r\n  * When I select BSC as network, the \"Data\" field is disabled, and I cannot use \"Send Offline\" for contract calls (on version v5.7.25)\r\n  * Other sidechains (e.g. XDAI) seem to work\r\n  * It would be very helpful (particularly with the current push for sidechains) to be able to use my offline wallet also to do contract calls with transaction data on BSC",
